    "body": "The `-rpcclienttimeout` option applies only to HTTP connections. When `bitcoin-cli` connects via IPC, the timeout is silently ignored. Clarify this in the help string.\r\n\r\nNoted by pinheadmz in https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/32297#pullrequestreview-3922849038",
